start_wsp.name: domicile.n.0
start_wsp.definition: (law) the residence where you have your permanent home or principal establishment and to where, whenever you are absent, you intend to return; every person is compelled to have one and only one domicile at a time

end_wsp.name: residence.n.0
end_wsp.definition: any address at which you dwell more than temporarily
